				>en vivo
			</span>
			<span><br /></span>
			<h2
				class="title -mt-2 flex justify-center text-wrap text-center text-2xl text-accent md:text-5xl"
			>
				Campo de Creadores
			</h2>
		</div>
	</a>

	<hr
		class="my-7 h-[2px] w-full min-w-[18rem] max-w-lg border-t-0 bg-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white to-transparent md:my-9"
	/>
</section>

<style>
	.title {
		font-family: "Akony", sans-serif;
	}
